1
00:00:18,240 --> 00:00:19,200
Commander.

2
00:00:19,840 --> 00:00:22,000
I am Song Qingzhou, the Deputy Warlord of Jiangcheng.

3
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:23,400
I am reporting to you that

4
00:00:23,520 --> 00:00:25,880
Song Huainan, the Warlord of Jiangcheng, has colluded with foreigners

5
00:00:25,880 --> 00:00:28,640
to secretly plant poppies in Jiangcheng,

6
00:00:29,080 --> 00:00:30,680
bringing harm to the people.

7
00:00:30,880 --> 00:00:31,940
Put down your guns.

8
00:00:40,840 --> 00:00:41,970
Take him to a doctor.

9
00:00:45,880 --> 00:00:47,440
Where is my home? Where is it?

10
00:00:47,440 --> 00:00:48,500
Who are you? Let go.

11
00:00:49,240 --> 00:00:51,280
Where did my brother go?

12
00:00:51,520 --> 00:00:53,680
Where did my father go? Go away.

13
00:00:56,280 --> 00:00:58,000
Brother.

14
00:01:04,560 --> 00:01:05,800
Don't lock me up.

15
00:01:05,800 --> 00:01:07,080
I beg you.

16
00:01:07,480 --> 00:01:10,800
I'll be good. Don't lock me up.

17
00:01:12,400 --> 00:01:13,520
Please.

18
00:01:34,320 --> 00:01:35,560
Yao Shengsheng?

19
00:01:40,479 --> 00:01:41,680
Who are you?

20
00:01:42,479 --> 00:01:43,840
I'm Song Huainan.

21
00:01:44,720 --> 00:01:45,520
Huainan.

22
00:01:45,600 --> 00:01:46,920
Take me home.

23
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:48,520
I can't find them.

24
00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:51,600
Take me to find them, okay?

25
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:54,000
Get some rest first.

26
00:01:54,479 --> 00:01:56,000
I'll take you back.

27
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:31,680
Isn't this the Governor?

28
00:02:32,200 --> 00:02:33,120
What brings you here?

29
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:34,160
This is...

30
00:02:34,160 --> 00:02:34,960
Song Huainan.

31
00:02:35,320 --> 00:02:37,800
You were ordered to protect the people of Jiangcheng,

32
00:02:37,800 --> 00:02:39,600
yet you secretly colluded with foreigners.

33
00:02:39,600 --> 00:02:41,320
What exactly is your ambition?

34
00:02:41,320 --> 00:02:42,079
Governor,

35
00:02:42,560 --> 00:02:45,040
don't believe these groundless rumors.

36
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:46,160
I really didn't.

37
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:47,720
Then come with me.

38
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:49,720
We'll see if they are rumors.

39
00:02:50,200 --> 00:02:50,680
Move.

40
00:02:54,320 --> 00:02:55,120
Let's go.

41
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:04,940
Commander,

42
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:06,780
you're finally out of prison.

43
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:09,760
The High Inspector had our plantation sealed off.

44
00:03:09,760 --> 00:03:10,720
The foreigners claim

45
00:03:10,720 --> 00:03:12,450
you're the one behind all this.

46
00:03:14,680 --> 00:03:16,880
Those foreign devils can't be trusted.

47
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:20,520
Good work.

48
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:29,320
Songsong, didn't you...

49
00:03:29,720 --> 00:03:32,680
What? Did you think I was still in prison?

50
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:35,280
I have my ways of getting out.

51
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:37,480
Song, don't be rash.

52
00:03:37,640 --> 00:03:38,960
I contacted the embassy.

53
00:03:38,960 --> 00:03:40,360
I can take you out of here.

54
00:03:40,560 --> 00:03:41,840
So considerate of me.

55
00:03:42,079 --> 00:03:42,880
Johnson.

56
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:45,480
Do you think I can still trust you?

57
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:47,520
Our affair was exposed,

58
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:49,079
but none of it is my fault.

59
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:49,920
Bullshit.

60
00:03:50,040 --> 00:03:51,440
You grow poppies and sell opium,

61
00:03:51,440 --> 00:03:52,900
and make me the scapegoat.

62
00:03:53,160 --> 00:03:54,520
In your dreams.

63
00:03:54,880 --> 00:03:57,240
Your brother, Song Qingzhou, turned us in.

64
00:03:57,240 --> 00:03:58,700
We should have killed him.

65
00:04:00,880 --> 00:04:02,840
Who do you think you are?

66
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:05,680
What I, Song Huainan, hate the most in this life

67
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:07,840
is those who betray me.

68
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:08,960
Song...

69
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:18,560
Song Qingzhou, you're next.

70
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:40,320
Luo Li.

71
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:53,840
Luo Li.

72
00:05:01,080 --> 00:05:02,480
Second Young Master, you're awake.

73
00:05:02,480 --> 00:05:03,400
Where is the Young Madam?

74
00:05:03,400 --> 00:05:04,440
I don't know.

75
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:07,720
Luoli.

76
00:05:09,200 --> 00:05:10,000
Young Master.

77
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:10,720
Luoli.

78
00:05:10,720 --> 00:05:12,720
Young Master, Second Young Master,

79
00:05:13,200 --> 00:05:14,080
you're seriously injured.

80
00:05:14,080 --> 00:05:15,080
You can't go out.

81
00:05:15,200 --> 00:05:16,680
You can't risk any more mishaps.

82
00:05:16,680 --> 00:05:17,480
Move.

83
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:17,760
Young Master.

84
00:05:17,760 --> 00:05:18,400
I'm going to find Luoli.

85
00:05:18,400 --> 00:05:19,530
Young Marshal Song,

86
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:22,240
Song Huainan escaped last night.

87
00:05:22,240 --> 00:05:23,040
What?

88
00:05:23,080 --> 00:05:23,880
Young Master.

89
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:25,800
I've sent men to search the whole city.

90
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:28,080
I've also increased the guard at the Song Residence.

91
00:05:28,080 --> 00:05:30,540
Watch out for Song Huainan sneaking back in.

92
00:05:31,120 --> 00:05:32,200
Understood.

93
00:05:35,840 --> 00:05:36,680
Let go.

94
00:05:37,080 --> 00:05:39,080
I can't leave Luoli out there alone.

95
00:05:40,320 --> 00:05:41,120
Young Master.

96
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:42,050
Don't follow me.

97
00:06:01,560 --> 00:06:02,360
Don't scream.

98
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:04,480
Haven't you always wanted to know

99
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:06,940
the whereabouts of your father and brother?

100
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:12,600
Are you taking me to see them?

101
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:13,320
Yes.

102
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:17,330
But you must cooperate with me.

103
00:06:38,280 --> 00:06:39,080
Luoli.

104
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,400
Luoli.

105
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:48,490
Where have you been?

106
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:50,240
I couldn't find you anywhere.

107
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:52,040
I was worried to death about you.

108
00:06:54,280 --> 00:06:56,240
I... I'm fine.

109
00:06:56,560 --> 00:06:58,020
Look, I'm perfectly fine.

110
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:02,300
Did Song Huainan give you a hard time?

111
00:07:02,480 --> 00:07:03,280
No.

112
00:07:17,320 --> 00:07:18,200
You seem

113
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:20,320
different today.

114
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:21,400
Really?

115
00:07:22,320 --> 00:07:23,440
In what way?

116
00:07:23,440 --> 00:07:24,500
Brother Qingzhou.

117
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:37,440
Yao Shengsheng. It really is you.

118
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:40,200
You may look exactly like Luoli,

119
00:07:40,200 --> 00:07:42,040
but she would never call me that.

120
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:45,280
Why are you pretending to be Luoli?

121
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:47,440
I'm pretending to be her?

122
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:50,800
She locked me in a dark room for months.

123
00:07:51,080 --> 00:07:52,400
She used my name,

124
00:07:52,400 --> 00:07:54,440
and my face to swindle people.

125
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:57,440
She even killed my father and brother.

126
00:07:57,880 --> 00:07:59,040
Who sent you?

127
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:00,520
Speak.

128
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:05,440
Song Huainan. He forced me.

129
00:08:05,440 --> 00:08:06,640
I knew it was him.

130
00:08:07,240 --> 00:08:08,900
What did he send you here to do?

131
00:08:08,960 --> 00:08:10,480
I... I don't know.

132
00:08:10,760 --> 00:08:13,080
He said he wanted to send someone home.

133
00:08:14,200 --> 00:08:15,560
To send Luoli home?

134
00:08:15,640 --> 00:08:17,720
I... I don't know.

135
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:19,960
Listen to me.

136
00:08:20,120 --> 00:08:22,480
Song Huainan is responsible for everything that happened to the Yao family.

137
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:24,210
It has nothing to do with Luoli.

138
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:52,640
Zhu Luoli.

139
00:08:54,280 --> 00:08:56,040
I really underestimated you.

140
00:08:58,080 --> 00:09:00,040
To think you single-handedly

141
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:04,800
turned the Song and Yao families

142
00:09:05,320 --> 00:09:07,240
upside down.

143
00:09:08,600 --> 00:09:09,480
Song Huainan.

144
00:09:10,160 --> 00:09:12,160
Didn't you bring this on yourself?

145
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:15,800
Gone. It's all gone.

146
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:19,920
I, Song Huainan, spent half my life fighting,

147
00:09:19,920 --> 00:09:22,250
painstakingly building this grand plan.

148
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:26,960
You ruined everything.

149
00:09:34,400 --> 00:09:35,200
Oh, right.

150
00:09:35,960 --> 00:09:37,920
And that stupid brother of mine.

151
00:09:38,720 --> 00:09:41,120
He actually betrayed me because of you.

152
00:09:48,760 --> 00:09:49,760
Zhu Luoli.

153
00:09:50,040 --> 00:09:53,120
Ten of your lives wouldn't be enough to pay for it.

154
00:10:15,400 --> 00:10:16,460
What are you doing?

155
00:10:17,440 --> 00:10:20,400
Didn't you want to take back everything belonging to the Zhu family?

156
00:10:20,400 --> 00:10:21,840
I'll give it all to you.

157
00:10:31,040 --> 00:10:34,680
Letting them be buried with you here,

158
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:38,000
consider it a worthy death.

159
00:10:40,280 --> 00:10:42,760
Song Huainan, are you crazy?
